To investigate the pattern of relative synonymous codon usage (RSCU) without the influence of amino acid composition among all samples, the RSCU values of codons in each ORF of NDV, H5N2 and DHV were calculated according to the formula of previous reports [31, 32].\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
